reviews.review_text: Despite the partly cloudy sound quality, which I sort of actually like as it heightens the soft overall tambral quality of the show, this is one of the pleasantest Dead tapes to listen to that I know of. Extremely interesting jams counterpointed by extreme mellowness, this is the epitome of everything I like about '76 Dead. A family folk-rock hippy band at its sweetest.
